column5: Brand new house built in later 2016 in the subdivision of Savannah surrounded by beautiful newer homes along with 3 pools. My house has 2900 square feet, 4 bedrooms, an office that can be used for work or even use the Euro bed as extra space for sleeping. Large rooms along with an open floor plan. I am starting back up after just moving to Texas from Cincinnati, Ohio where I was the top rated host while living their. I am very close to shopping, restaurants, venues, and much more.
